import React from "react";
import {MonsterCard} from "..";
import {Container,Row,Col} from "react-bootstrap";
const MonsterList = () => {
    return(
       <Container>
           <Row>
               <input className="input-search" type="text" placeholder="میتونی در من جستوجو کنی :)"/>
               <Col> zxa</Col>
           </Row>
           <Row>
               <Col xs={3}>
                   <MonsterCard/>
               </Col>
               <Col xs={3}>
                   <MonsterCard/>
               </Col>
               <Col xs={3}>
                   <MonsterCard/>
               </Col>
               <Col xs={3}>
                   <MonsterCard/>
               </Col>

           </Row>
       </Container>
    )
}

export default MonsterList;
